Meet <b>Tereza</b>, our Citizen of the Week!<br><br>Tereza's Westridge home is well-known in her scenic neighborhood.  She can often be seen maintaining the front lawn of <a href='/home/?user=legna07'>54607 Sierra Mesa Road</a> and greeting her neighbors. Since June 4, 2006, Tereza has impressed everyone she meets with her smarts and charm.<br><br>Tereza has a great sense of humor and is always making people laugh. She likes to instant message with friends and hang out at the movie theater. She also loves music, heavy metal, pop, and modern rock in particular. And she's certainly not shy about singing and dancing along to her favorite tunes! Tereza is very outgoing, a trait that her friends really admire.<br><br>Feel free to stop by Tereza's home and ask about her music collection. She has also been seen at the Millsberry Recording Studio [link] laying down some tracks of her own. No matter what she's doing, Tereza puts in a lot of effort and enthusiasm. Her interests often change, but her drive to succeed and her thirst for knowledge never do!  <br><br>Thanks for being a good citizen, Tereza, and congratulations on being named Citizen of the Week!<br><br></div>
